reviewText: A must have (if you are Venezuelan). Excellent video , production and audio.

Guaco outdid themselves once more... Guaco... La Superbanda de Venezuela... A must from Venezuelans and a very special recommendation to anyone who wants to enjoy good latin music with a jazz, salsa, funk twist. With many guest from over the decades including Kiara, Jorge Luis Chacn, Nelson Arrieta, Luis Enrique, y Gilberto Santa Rosa among others is a delight. Enjoy!!!

For those of you Guaqueros that like "La Super Banda-GUACO ". This is a must for your collection.  DVD is very well recorded, the sound is awesome, and all of the songs are truly a jewel.  Love this band!
